   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Saving the honeybee one beekeeper at a time!</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Spikenard Honeybee Sanctuary is raising funds for scholarships, children&apos;s programs, and new workshops so that more and more individuals can learn methods of sustainable beekeeping that contribute towards saving the honeybee.  While most blame collapsing honeybee populations on pesticide companies, lack of habitat, and invasive parasites, we recognize that if we, as beekeepers, do not change our ways, our children are likely to grow up in a world without bees, without flowers, without fruits.</narrative>
  </description>
